              <decoDesc>
                <decoNote xml:id="decoNote1" type="illustration"><locus from="83b" to="83b"/>
                  <p>On fol. 83b there is a coloured Cross, surrounded by a nimbus.</p>
                </decoNote>
              </decoDesc>
              <additions>
                <list>
                  <item n="1" xml:id="addition1" syriaca-tags="scribal-colophon ownership-inscription"><locus from="83b"/>
                    <p>According to the notes on the same page, this manuscript was written by a person named <persName>George</persName>, and belonged to the <placeName>convent of Silvanus</placeName>, near <placeName>Damascus</placeName>, having been purchased for it by the abbat.</p>
                    <p><quote xml:lang="syr">ܨܠܘ ܡܪܝ ܥܠ ܓܘܪܓܝܣ ܒܨܝܪܐ ܕܟܬ̣ܒ ܕܢܬܚܢܢ ܒܝܘܡ ܕܝܢ̣ܐ ܐܡܝܢ.܀ܐܝܬܘܗܝ ܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ ܕܥܘܡܪܐ ܩܕܝܫܐ ܕܣܝܠܘܢܐ̣. ܕܫܘܠܛܢܐ ܕܕܡܣܩܘܣ ܡܕܝܢܬܐ. ܐܠܐ ܟܠ ܕܫ̇ܩܠ ܠܗ ܒܚܕ ܡܢ ܙܢ̈ܝܢ: ܘܠܐ ܡ̇ܦܢܐ ܠܗ ܠܥܘܡܪܐ[ܐ ܕܐܡܝܪ:] ܥܠ ܡܠܬܐ ܕܚܝܠ̣ܬܐ ܘܙܝܥ̣ܬܐ ܕ[ܐܠܗܐ] ܥ̇ܒܪ܀܀ܙܒ̣ܝܢ ܕܝܢ ܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ̣ . . . ܩܫܝܫܐ ܘܪܝܫܕܝܪܐ ܕܥܘܡܪ[ܐ] . . . ܠܝܘܬܪܢܐ ܕܚ̈ܝܘܗܝ ܘܠ . . . ܕܥܢ̣ܕܘ ܒܗ . . .  ܕܫܪ. . . </quote></p></item>
                  <item n="2" xml:id="addition2">
                    <p>Foll. <locus>1, 2</locus>, <locus>63</locus>, and <locus>66</locus> are paper leaves of the <date from="1100" to="1200">xiith cent.</date></p>
                  </item>
                </list>
              </additions>
